---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Stash">
  <div id="app">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="lock-icon">🔒</div>
        <h1>No Data Collection</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Stash Privacy Policy</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p class="intro">
          <strong>Stash</strong> is designed with privacy as a core principle. 
          Here's what you need to know:
        </p>

        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span><strong>No personal data is collected.</strong> We don't track you, store cookies, or gather any information about you.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span><strong>All sharing happens locally in your browser.</strong> Stash selection and link generation occur entirely on your device.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span><strong>No data is transmitted to external servers.</strong> The only thing sent is the share link you choose to send.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Shared links contain only tab URLs and titles.</strong> These are user-selected and encoded directly into the link itself.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Links expire based on your settings.</strong> You can configure expiry to 24 hours, 7 days, 30 days, or never. Shared content cannot be accessed once a link expires.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="summary">
          <p>Stash doesn't have servers, databases, or analytics. It's a simple tool that works entirely in your browser.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  #app {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--background);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--background);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    max-width: 600px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .lock-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .content {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--foreground);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
  }

  .policy-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
  }

  .policy-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--foreground);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .policy-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .check {
    color: var(--success);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .summary {
    background: var(--muted);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 16px;
  }

  .summary p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    background: var(--muted);
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    margin: 16px 0 0 0;
  }
</style>
